ygData.messageBody:
Here is a subject we haven't touch on and one I have been wondering about.
I am level 15 and have pretty much got a full set of banded armor. However,
I don't have any earrings, and the rings I wear are just Dervish Cutthroat
rings which add to your dexterity. What kind of jewelry is everyone wearing
and what magic effects do they have? In addition, can you buy this jewelry
at the shops or do you have to kill certain characters to get it?

Grod
15th Level
Innoruuk Server
